            <abstract label="Abstract:">Records include account book of goods delivered, raw
                materials &amp; dyestuffs; also goods sent elsewhere for finishing, 1845-1849;
                payroll &amp; manufacturing accounts, few dye receipts, 1845- 1851; a work and time
                book, 1845-48; weave room time book, 1851-1852; weaving records, per employee,
                1849-1850.</abstract>
